OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772903477
OL,3,CCordon at Tebay Services as police
OL,4,Cexamine vehicle following fatal
OL,5,Ccollision
OL,7,FA police cordon has been in place at
OL,8,FTebay Services in Cumbria, as officers
OL,9,Fexamine a vehicle they believe was
OL,10,Finvolved in a fatal collision on the
OL,11,FM6.
OL,13,FAt around 2.50am on Saturday (7
OL,14,FMarch), police were called to reports
OL,15,Fof a serious collision on the
OL,16,Fmotorway, between junctions 21 and
OL,17,F21A, near Warrington in Cheshire.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
