OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772903477
OL,3,CCordon at Tebay Services as police
OL,4,Cexamine vehicle following fatal
OL,5,Ccollision
OL,7,FOfficers found that a pedestrian had
OL,8,Fbeen struck by several vehicles, and
OL,9,Fthe pedestrian was pronounced dead at
OL,10,Fthe scene.
OL,12,FRoad closures were put in place there,
OL,13,Fand also further north between
OL,14,Fjunctions 28 and 30 in Lancashire.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, officers confirmed that a
OL,17,Fcordon was in place at Tebay Services
OL,18,Fto allow for the forensic examination
OL,19,Fof a vehicle that is believed to have
OL,20,Fbeen involved.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
