OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772903477
OL,3,CCordon at Tebay Services as police
OL,4,Cexamine vehicle following fatal
OL,5,Ccollision
OL,7,FEnquiries are continuing, and anyone
OL,8,Fwith any information is being asked to
OL,9,Fcontact Cheshire Police who are
OL,10,Fleading the investigation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/3
